{"id":"4a2f1789-edce-45d1-b574-f01c1fc9c124","name":"Aurore Cassel","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 82, 0)\">\"ᴛʜɪꜱ 'ᴘᴀʀᴛʏ' ɪꜱ ᴘᴀᴛʜᴇᴛɪᴄ..\"<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7qjrVcX.png\" style=\"\" draggable=\"true\"></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ꜰʟɪʀᴛᴀᴛɪᴏᴜꜱ, ᴛʜʀɪʟʟ-ꜱᴇᴇᴋɪɴɢ, ɴᴇᴛʀᴜɴɴᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🥃</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ꜰᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ ꜰᴏʀᴍɪᴅᴀʙʟᴇ ꜱᴋɪʟʟꜱ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ɴᴇᴛʀᴜɴɴᴇʀ ᴀɴᴅ ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴇɴᴄʜᴀɴᴛ ꜰᴏʀ ᴇxᴄɪᴛᴇᴍᴇɴᴛ, ᴀᴜʀᴏʀᴇ ᴄᴀꜱꜱᴇʟ ꜰᴏʀᴍꜱ ʜᴀʟꜰ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ɪɴꜰᴀᴍᴏᴜꜱ ᴅᴜᴏ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ \"ꜱᴋʏʟɪɢʜᴛ.\" ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴀꜱꜱɪᴏɴ ꜰᴏʀ ʜɪɢʜ-ꜱᴛᴀᴋᴇꜱ ɪɴᴛʀɪɢᴜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴍᴀᴛᴄʜᴇᴅ ᴏɴʟʏ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ʟᴏᴠᴇ ꜰᴏʀ ᴀᴅᴠᴇɴᴛᴜʀᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀɴ ᴜɴᴀᴘᴏʟᴏɢᴇᴛɪᴄ ᴇᴍʙʀᴀᴄᴇ ᴏꜰ ʟɪꜰᴇ'ꜱ ꜰɪɴᴇꜱᴛ ɪɴᴅᴜʟɢᴇɴᴄᴇꜱ. ʜᴇʀ ꜰɪᴇʀʏ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟɪᴛʏ ꜱᴇᴛꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴀᴘᴀʀᴛ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ʜᴇʀ ʙʀᴏᴛʜᴇʀ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ꜱᴇᴅᴜᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏᴍᴀɴ ᴡʜᴏ ᴇꜰꜰᴏʀᴛʟᴇꜱꜱʟʏ ᴅʀᴀᴡꜱ ᴀᴛᴛᴇɴᴛɪᴏɴ, ᴄᴀᴘᴛɪᴠᴀᴛɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴘᴀɴʏ ᴏꜰ ʜɪɢʜ-ᴘʀᴏꜰɪʟᴇ ꜰɪɢᴜʀᴇꜱ ᴀʟᴏɴɢ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀɴ ᴇxᴛʀᴀᴠᴀɢᴀɴᴛ ʟɪꜰᴇꜱᴛʏʟᴇ ᴍᴀʀᴋᴇᴅ ʙʏ ʟᴜxᴜʀʏ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘᴀꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀᴛᴇ ꜱᴇx... ʟᴏᴛꜱ ᴏꜰ ꜱᴇx. ᴅᴇꜱᴘɪᴛᴇ ʜᴇʀ ᴘʀᴏᴠᴏᴄᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ, ᴀᴜʀᴏʀᴇ'ꜱ ɪɴᴛᴇʟʟɪɢᴇɴᴄᴇ ꜱʜᴏᴜʟᴅ ɴᴏᴛ ʙᴇ ᴜɴᴅᴇʀᴇꜱᴛɪᴍᴀᴛᴇᴅ. ᴡɪᴛʜ ʜᴇʀ ꜱʜᴀʀᴘ ᴍɪɴᴅ, ᴄᴜɴɴɪɴɢ ɪɴᴛᴇʟʟᴇᴄᴛ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴍᴀɴɪᴘᴜʟᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ ꜱᴋɪʟʟꜱ, ꜱʜᴇ ʀᴇᴍᴀɪɴꜱ ᴀ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇ ᴛᴏ ʙᴇ ʀᴇᴄᴋᴏɴᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ꜱᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4ce94b08-7caa-47ae-afc8-0a07926df53f_character-aurore-cassel-nsfw\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/fhqi9x.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/fhqi9x.png\" target=\"_blank\">ɴꜱꜰᴡ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ</a>: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4ce94b08-7caa-47ae-afc8-0a07926df53f_character-aurore-cassel-nsfw\" target=\"_blank\">ʟᴇᴛ'ꜱ ɢᴇᴛ ɪᴛ ᴏɴ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/ZxGMK9Hb6n8?si=tqMgEgjBQkY601Ii\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/s16a99.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴋᴇɴᴅʀɪᴄᴋ qᴜᴏᴛᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀʏ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/ZxGMK9Hb6n8?si=tqMgEgjBQkY601Ii\" target=\"_blank\">ɪ ꜱᴀɪᴅ ɪ'ᴍ ɢᴇᴇᴋᴇᴅ &amp; ɪ'ᴍ ꜰɪʀᴇᴅ ᴜᴘ. ᴀʟʟ ɪ ᴡᴀɴᴛ ᴛᴏɴɪɢʜᴛ ɪꜱ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ᴛᴏ ɢᴇᴛ ʜɪɢʜ ᴜᴘ.</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴏʏᴀʟᴛʏ ꜰᴛ. ʀɪʜᴀɴɴᴀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴀᴍɴ, 2017</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/2prmle.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/2prmle.png\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/bg06c5.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/bg06c5.png\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ixmlyd.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ixmlyd.png\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪɪɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/MentorMiyagi?gameId=3333\" target=\"_blank\">ᴍᴇɴᴛᴏʀᴍɪʏᴀɢɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-ali","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"NtECkFqZWU_5YbGg87h2i.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1745,"messages":26188,"created_at":"2025-06-17T06:35:53.802075+00:00"}